[gd_scene load_steps=70 format=3]

; SAND — Sun-baked desert with a climbable pyramid, ruin courtyard, oasis,
; hidden pyramid interior, and scarab easter egg. Player is ~1.5m penguin.
; Landmarks: Dune field, Quicksand Pit, 4-tier Pyramid w/ interior chamber,
;   Ruin Courtyard (8 columns), Oasis, Obelisk, Chameleon cave, Scarab shrine.
; Tiers: dunes / pyramid mid-tiers / pyramid apex + obelisk.
; Content: 13 enemies, 30 yellow coins, 8 red coins (one per ruin column),
;   2 stars (apex + vault), 2 one-ups, 1 metal cap.

